🟢 Language ➡ C
🟢 Topic ➡ Decision Control 


📘  Decision Control Instructions 
👉 Used to make decisions and control the flow of execution based on conditions.

🔹 if Statement
Executes code only if the condition is true.
if (condition) {
    // true block
}



🔹 if...else
Choose between two blocks based on condition.
if (condition) {
    // true block
} else {
    // false block
}




🔹 else if Ladder
Checks multiple conditions in sequence.
if (cond1) {
    // block 1
} else if (cond2) {
    // block 2
} else {
    // default block
}




🔹 Ternary Operator ? :
Shorthand for if...else.

(condition) ? value_if_true : value_if_false;





🔹 Logical Operators
Used to combine or compare conditions:

&& (AND)
|| (OR)
! (NOT)


